  )
Maintainer: Akiru Kato <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: The goal of ldccr package is to make easy to use Japanese
    language resources. This package provides parsers for several Japanese
    corpora that are free or open licensed and a downloader of zipped text
    files published on Aozora Bunko.
